events.text:
I might have one more favor needed from you. Our Officer of Affairs Naggob needs this wood.
He needs to ship this off to Khozgrogal, in case you haven't heard: the biggest city of the orcs!
I here stacked this wood nice for him, I'd like you to go and tell to come and fetch it.
My wood still here! I reckon you haven't spoke to him! Now git!

Dhabu sent you? Where's the shipment at? He wants us to go and get it?!
Aghhh!!! I've had it with that good for nothing greenskin. I'll send muscle to go and get it.
